== Build Documentation ==
=== Dependencies ===
==== Linux (Debian) ====
* build-essential
* ant
* subversion
* libgtk2.0-dev
* libglib1.2-dev
* libidl-dev
* libxt-dev
* gcc-3.4
* g++-3.4
* zip
* unzip
* fakeroot
* dpkg-deb
* a Java JDK for ant (java-gcj-compat-dev, sun-java6-jdk, openjdk-6-jdk,...)

==== Windows ====
See http://developer.mozilla.org/en/docs/Windows_Build_Prerequisites

=== Building ===
  // Get packager from SVN
 $ svn co https://admisource.gouv.fr/svn/milimail/trunk/packager milimail
 (permanently accept SSL certificate if asked)
 $ cd milimail
  // Build and package milimail and extensions
 $ ant build-all

  // OR: build and package milimail
 $ ant extract-milimail update-milimail build-milimail package-milimail
  // OR: build and package extensions
 $ ant package-extensions
